description.plain: Nya Kilgore, known professionally as NextYoungin, or Daddy Kaine, is an American rapper who first appeared on “3 Musketeers” by artist ppcocaine. Pronouns are she/her/daddy. Her bio is usually “Ha, ion even rap 👽” .
